{
  "texts": [
    "This dataset covers a diverse set of 10 tasks across 14 different datasets, encompassing eight programming languages, and it serves as a platform for evaluating and comparing models in the field of code generation.",
    "Challenges and opportunitiesIn this section, we highlight some challenges and opportunities for future research in deep learning techniques for code generation.",
    "Challenges• Unsafe code generation.",
    "Deep learning techniques, especially recently proposed LLMs, are (pre-) trained on massive code bases and then applied to code generation.",
    "The code bases may include vulnerable code snippets that lead to generation of unsafe code."
  ]
}